  "3100690": {
    "name": "废土镖客：禁区快递",
    "steam_appid": 3100690,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br><br><strong>《废土镖客：禁区快递》 是一款让玩家身临其境的后世界末日卡车模拟游戏，玩家可以在危险而荒凉的景观中穿行。这款游戏受到此类游戏的高能量气场和粗犷美学的启发，玩家需要在一个崩溃的世界里建立和管理自己的送货公司，是否生存取决于你的合理规划，以及技能和力量。</strong><br><br><strong>游戏玩法：</strong><br><br><strong>公司建设：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>目标：玩家从一辆普通卡车和一家小型送货公司开始，最终目标是发展成为遍布荒野的主导物流帝国。<br></li><li>任务：管理资源、雇佣司机、维护和升级车队，并规划高效的送货路线。成功的送货将带来更高的利润，从而实现进一步的扩张和提升。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/bc6df68f4afda460941d02bcd92f8b4a.poster.avif?t=1758908824\" width=620 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/bc6df68f4afda460941d02bcd92f8b4a.webm?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/bc6df68f4afda460941d02bcd92f8b4a.mp4?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>卡车定制和升级：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>定制：玩家可以使用各种零件和外观来个性化他们的卡车，打造一支独特而强大的车队。<br></li><li>升级：使用更好的发动机、强化装甲、更大的货舱和专业设备增强卡车以应对恶劣环境。<br></li><li>武器和防御：为卡车配备各种炮塔、尖刺和其他防御措施，以抵御道路上的土匪和其他威胁。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/a6aa597ff27d0563fbe5dd83b7cdcfa5.poster.avif?t=1758908824\" width=620 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/a6aa597ff27d0563fbe5dd83b7cdcfa5.webm?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/a6aa597ff27d0563fbe5dd83b7cdcfa5.mp4?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>战斗和保护：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>土匪：定期击退试图劫持贵重货物的流动土匪的袭击。<br></li><li>炮塔：战略性地安装和升级炮塔和其他武器，以在运输过程中保护您的货物。<br></li><li>战术：参与实时战斗，快速做出决策以智取胜并击败攻击者。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/6d7c2b6a7d8057c659e7ca0f04dd5b39.poster.avif?t=1758908824\" width=620 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/6d7c2b6a7d8057c659e7ca0f04dd5b39.webm?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/6d7c2b6a7d8057c659e7ca0f04dd5b39.mp4?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>地形和环境挑战：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>动态天气：面对影响驾驶、能见度和道路状况的各种天气条件。<br></li><li>困难地形：穿越泥坑、流沙、岩石小径和狭窄的越野路径，这些都考验驾驶技能和卡车的耐用性。<br></li><li>障碍：处理可能阻碍路线并需要绕行的路障、倒塌的建筑物和自然灾害。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/be3e2381199104084da68973687f3d3c.poster.avif?t=1758908824\" width=620 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/be3e2381199104084da68973687f3d3c.webm?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/be3e2381199104084da68973687f3d3c.mp4?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>任务和合同：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>多样化的合同：接受并完成各种各样的运送任务，从运输必需物资到护送宝贵的资产穿越荒地。<br></li><li>声誉：成功的运送和强大的战斗力将帮助你提高声誉，吸引更高薪和更有声望的合同。</li></ul><br><br><strong>主要特点：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>逼真的卡车：体验逼真的驾驶机制，你需要考虑经过大量改装后的卡车重量、平衡和操控性。<br></li><li>沙盒：探索广阔的开放世界地图，其中充满了隐藏的地点、资源以及搜寻和交易的机会。<br></li><li>生存：管理燃料、卡车状况和其他生存资源，以确保您的运输事业在恶劣的环境中顺利进行。<br></li><li>视觉和音频设计：通过细致的图形、动态灯光和紧张和兴奋的配乐，让玩家沉浸在坚韧不拔的反乌托邦氛围中。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/9ab23a83ffd849038c60dcca06709e05.poster.avif?t=1758908824\" width=620 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/9ab23a83ffd849038c60dcca06709e05.webm?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/9ab23a83ffd849038c60dcca06709e05.mp4?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《废土镖客：禁区快递》 将高风险卡车运输的刺激与战略管理和激烈的战斗相结合，在精心打造的后世界末日世界中提供独特而引人入胜的体验。您会接受挑战并成为最终的送货巨头，还是荒地吞噬您和您的梦想？旅程即将开始。</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/b47566200bdc6f7f14f4664b7847e410.poster.avif?t=1758908824\" width=616 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/b47566200bdc6f7f14f4664b7847e410.webm?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100690/extras/b47566200bdc6f7f14f4664b7847e410.mp4?t=1758908824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
